     * - TEMP < 47: turn heater ON (state HEATING)
     * - TEMP > 52: turn heater OFF (state SAFE_OFF)
     * - 47 <= TEMP < 50: hold previous safe actuator state (state HOLDING)
     * - 50 <= TEMP <= 52:
