         * - TEMP < 47: turn heater ON (state HEATING)
         * - TEMP > 52: turn heater OFF (state SAFE_OFF)
         * - 47 <= TEMP < 50: hold previous safe actuator state (always SAFE_OFF, state HOLDING)
         * - 50 <= TEMP <= 52:
         *   - If rising temp: turn heater OFF early, treat as HOLDING
         *   - If not rising: hold previous safe actuator state (HOLDING)
         */

